reviewText: It was great fun seeing this Scott movie in color for the first time.  I had only seen in in black and white a couple times before, in the days before color tv,  This time I noticed that he was riding a big sorrel that might have been the daddy for his palomino Starlight that he rode in most of his later westerns.  It was a fun western based on a Zane Grey story and with all the action that we came to expect from westerns made at that time.  A great addition to my collection.
